Class MainFrameModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • pacman_ultimater.project_base.gui_swing.model.MainFrameModel
  • public class MainFrameModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Class acting as application's model. Holds together all of application's original labels. Provides several methods for controllers' usage.
